  (21, ' Regulatory Data Administrator Internship', ' regulatory-data-administrator-internship', ' People & Corporate Affairs Directorate', ' Full Time', ' https://apply.workable.com/pt-link-net-tbk-1/j/D7956B0D0F/apply/', ' Tangerang, Indonesia', ' <ul><li>Assist in payment process.</li><li>Assist in collecting and organizing regulatory data from various sources.</li><li>Support the preparation and submission of regulatory reports and documentation.</li><li>Help maintain databases that track regulatory compliance activities and deadlines.</li><li>Participate in improving data management processes for regulatory requirements.</li><li>Assisting in preparing data for annual, quarterly, monthly, and weekly report.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Current student or recent graduate in Law, Public Policy, Business Administration, Accounting, Electrical Engineering, Computer Science, or a related field.</li><li>Strong attention to detail with the ability to organize and manage data effectively.</li><li>Proficiency in Microsoft Office Suite (especially Excel) and familiarity with data management tools.</li><li>Good analytical and research skills.</li><li>Excellent communication skills, both written and verbal.</li><li>Willing to work in <strong>Karawaci, Tangerang</strong>.</li></ul><p><strong>Benefits</strong></p><ul><li>Allowance</li><li>Hybrid</li></ul>', ' <ul><li>Membantu dalam proses pembayaran.</li><li>Membantu dalam mengumpulkan dan mengorganisir data regulasi dari berbagai sumber.</li><li>Mendukung persiapan dan pengajuan laporan serta dokumentasi regulasi.</li><li>Membantu memelihara database yang melacak aktivitas dan tenggat kepatuhan regulasi.</li><li>Berpartisipasi dalam peningkatan proses manajemen data untuk kebutuhan regulasi.</li><li>Membantu menyiapkan data untuk laporan tahunan, triwulanan, bulanan, dan mingguan.</li></ul><p><strong>Persyaratan</strong></p><ul><li>Mahasiswa aktif atau lulusan baru dari jurusan Hukum, Kebijakan Publik