  (27, ' Employee & Industrial Relations Internship', ' employee-industrial-relations-internship', ' People & Corporate Affairs Directorate', ' Contract', ' https://apply.workable.com/pt-link-net-tbk-1/j/14F99AE7C2/apply/', ' Tangerang, Indonesia', ' <ul><li>Support the Employee &amp; Industrial Relations team in various administrative and operational tasks.</li><li>Support design matters for all Employee &amp; Industrial Relation activities.</li><li>Support Employee &amp; Industrial Relation project &amp; events.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Currently pursuing or recently completed a degree in Visual Communication Design.</li><li>Proficient in Graphic Design (Flyer &amp; Video), Copy Writing.</li><li>Familiar with organizing an event/webinar/being a committee at your school.</li><li>Familiar with Canva.</li><li>Interest in employee relations and human resource management.</li><li>Strong communication and interpersonal skills to effectively engage with diverse teams.</li><li>Internship period : 6 months.</li><li>Willing to work in <strong>Cyber Park Karawaci, Tangerang</strong>, <strong>Banten</strong>.</li></ul><p><strong>Benefits</strong></p><ul><li>Meal &amp; transportation allowance</li></ul>', ' <ul><li>Mendukung tim Employee &amp; Industrial Relations dalam berbagai tugas administratif dan operasional.</li><li>Mendukung kebutuhan desain untuk seluruh aktivitas Employee &amp; Industrial Relations.</li><li>Mendukung proyek dan acara Employee &amp; Industrial Relations.</li></ul><p><strong>Persyaratan</strong></p><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Sedang menempuh atau baru menyelesaikan pendidikan di bidang Desain Komunikasi Visual.</li><li>Mahir dalam Desain Grafis (Flyer &amp; Video) serta Copywriting.</li><li>Familiar dalam mengorganisir acara/webinar atau pernah menjadi panitia di kampus/sekolah.</li><li>Familiar dengan Canva.</li><li>Memiliki ketertarikan pada employee relations dan manajemen sumber daya manusia.</li><li>Memiliki kemampuan komunikasi dan interpersonal yang baik untuk berinteraksi dengan berbagai tim.</li><li>Periode magang: 6 bulan.</li><li>Bersedia bekerja di <strong>Cyber Park Karawaci, Tangerang, Banten</strong>.</li></ul><p><strong>Benefit</strong></p><ul><li>Uang makan &amp; transportasi</li></ul>', NULL, NULL, ' active', NULL, ' 2025-11-28 12:40:01', ' 2025-11-28 12:40:01', ' admin@gmail.com', NULL),
  (28, ' Graphic Design Internship', ' graphic-design-internship', ' People & Corporate Affairs Directorate', ' Full Time', ' https://apply.workable.com/pt-link-net-tbk-1/j/BDD85B5025/apply/', ' Tangerang, Indonesia', ' <ul><li>Support the Corporate Culture &amp; Engagement (CCE) team in developing high-quality visual content for Employer Branding purposes, including managing content for platforms such as @lifeatlinknet on Instagram and PT Link Net Tbk on LinkedIn, as well as for Culture &amp; Engagement programs.</li><li>Contribute to the Culture &amp; Engagement team''s efforts by assisting with content ideation, visualization, and design execution.</li><li>Provide support to the CCE team in planning and executing corporate events, programs, and activities.</li><li>Collaborate with the CCE intern to create engaging content, including capturing and documenting moments during company events.</li><li>Keep up-to-date with the latest design trends and advancements in design software.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><p><strong>Internship Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Currently pursuing or recently completed a degree in Graphic Design, Visual Arts, or a related field.</li><li>Proficient in Adobe Creative Suite (Photoshop, Illustrator, InDesign).</li><li>Strong creative and artistic skills with attention to detail.</li><li>Good understanding of design principles such as layout, typography, and color theory.</li><li>Ability to take direction and work collaboratively in a team environment.</li><li>Strong communication skills and ability to meet deadlines.</li><li>Experience with web design and video creation (optional, but a plus).</li><li>A portfolio showcasing relevant design work is required.</li><li>Willing to work in <strong>Karawaci, Tangerang</strong>.</li></ul>', ' <ul><li>Mendukung tim Corporate Culture &amp; Engagement (CCE) dalam mengembangkan konten visual berkualitas tinggi untuk keperluan Employer Branding, termasuk mengelola konten untuk platform seperti @lifeatlinknet di Instagram dan PT Link Net Tbk di LinkedIn, serta untuk program Culture &amp; Engagement.</li><li>Berkontribusi pada upaya tim Culture &amp; Engagement dengan membantu proses ideasi konten, visualisasi, dan eksekusi desain.</li><li>Memberikan dukungan kepada tim CCE dalam merencanakan dan melaksanakan acara, program, dan aktivitas perusahaan.</li><li>Berkolaborasi dengan intern CCE lainnya untuk membuat konten yang menarik, termasuk mengambil gambar dan mendokumentasikan momen selama acara perusahaan.</li><li>Mengikuti perkembangan terbaru dalam tren desain dan kemajuan perangkat lunak desain.</li></ul><p><strong>Persyaratan</strong></p><p><strong>Internship Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Sedang menempuh atau baru menyelesaikan pendidikan di bidang Desain Grafis, Seni Visual, atau bidang terkait.</li><li>Mahir menggunakan Adobe Creative Suite (Photoshop, Illustrator, InDesign).</li><li>Memiliki kreativitas tinggi dan kemampuan artistik dengan perhatian pada detail.</li><li>Memahami prinsip-prinsip desain seperti layout, tipografi, dan teori warna.</li><li>Mampu menerima arahan dan bekerja kolaboratif dalam tim.</li><li>Memiliki kemampuan komunikasi yang baik dan mampu memenuhi tenggat waktu.</li><li>Pengalaman dalam web design dan pembuatan video (opsional, menjadi nilai tambah).</li><li>Wajib memiliki portofolio yang menunjukkan hasil desain relevan.</li><li>Bersedia bekerja di <strong>Karawaci, Tangerang</strong>.</li></ul>', NULL, NULL, ' active', NULL, ' 2025-11-28 12:42:08', ' 2025-11-28 12:42:08', ' admin@gmail.com', NULL),
  (29, ' Media Content Internship', ' media-content-internship', ' Media Co Directorate', ' Full Time', ' https://apply.workable.com/pt-link-net-tbk-1/j/F76016454D/apply/', ' South Jakarta City, Indonesia', ' <p><strong>Content highlights all platforms&nbsp;</strong></p><ul><li>Assist in selecting and organizing content that needs to be placed on channels&nbsp;</li><li>Checking the accuracy of Content Highlights&nbsp;</li><li>Process to be documented</li></ul><p><strong>User experience on STB models, FMX</strong></p><ul><li>Identifying and mapping the flows for current navigations</li><li>support analyze&nbsp;the viewer journey on platforms</li><li>Assist in creating content layouts for on-screen displays based on other competitive platforms&nbsp;</li></ul><p><strong>Process mapping&nbsp;</strong></p><ul><li>Documentation of all processes within Media Co for B2B operations</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Fresh Graduate / Final Year Student from Visual Communication Design, Information Systems, Informatics Engineering, or any related major.</li><li>Basic understanding of UI/UX principles, and user journey mapping.</li><li>Proficient in Microsoft Office Suite (Word, Excel, PowerPoint), VISIO, or any tool to represent the findings.</li><li>Familiar with content data presentation.</li><li>Strong communication and interpersonal skills to effectively engage with diverse teams.</li><li>Internship period : 3 months.</li><li>Willing to work in <strong>Centennial, South Jakarta</strong>.</li></ul><p><strong>Benefits</strong></p><ul><li>Allowance</li><li>Hybrid</li></ul>', ' <ul><li>Menyoroti konten di seluruh platform.</li><li>Membantu dalam memilih dan mengatur konten yang perlu ditampilkan di berbagai saluran.</li><li>Memeriksa akurasi Content Highlights.</li><li>Mendokumentasikan proses yang dilakukan.</li><li>Mengamati pengalaman pengguna pada model STB, FMX.</li><li>Mengidentifikasi dan memetakan alur navigasi saat ini.</li><li>Mendukung analisis per