  (27, ' Link Net Reports Record High Revenue, Operating Profit & Net Profit Numbers In 1h 2017', NULL, ' https://www.linknet.co.id/storage/files/images/media_activities/381c5382acbb747c37d5bb10637e6e6745ccd6e2.jpg', ' link-net-reports-record-high-revenue-operating-profit-net-profit-numbers-in-1h-2017', ' Link Net Reports Record High Revenue, Operating Profit & Net Profit Numbers In 1h 2017', NULL, ' Muhammad Daffa Prayodi', ' <p>July 31, 2017</p>

<p><strong>1H 2017 Results Highlights<br />
&bull; +18.5% growth in revenues to Rp1.65 trillion<br />
&bull; +23% growth in Operating Profit to Rp662 billion<br />
&bull; +23% growth in net profit to Rp490 billion<br />
&bull; 1.9 million total homes passed</strong></p>

<p>PT Link Net Tbk (&ldquo;<strong>Link Net</strong>&rdquo; or the &ldquo;<strong>Company</strong>&rdquo;; stock code: &ldquo;LINK&rdquo;) continued on a strong growth<br />
trajectory in the second quarter of 2017 (&ldquo;<strong>2Q 2017</strong>&rdquo;), announcing their highest first half (&ldquo;<strong>1H 2017</strong>&rdquo;)<br />
Revenue, Operating Profit and Net Profit results in the company&rsquo;s history.</p>

<p>Revenue in the first half grew at +18.5% Year on Year to Rp1.65tn, as The Company increased<br />
its ARPU to Rp419k.</p>

<p>The Company experienced continued margin expansion in 1H 2017 as our high ARPU fueled<br />
strong revenue growth while costs were kept under control. The Company&rsquo;s Operating Profit grew<br />
23% Year on Year in 1H 2017 to Rp662bn. Net Profit grew to Rp490bn in 1H 2017 while the first<br />
half net profit margin expanded to 29.7% from 28.5% in 1H 2016.</p>

<p>The Company continued to expand its network in 2Q 2017 adding an additional 47,000 homes,<br />
taking the total number of homes passed as at 1H 2017 to 1.9 million. ARPU edged higher to<br />
Rp419k as customers continue to enthusiastically embrace value added services and upgrade to<br />
higher value packages.</p>

<p>The Company&rsquo;s robust financial and operational results are a reflection of the sustained demand<br />
for high quality cable television and broadband internet services in Indonesia&rsquo;s high GDP zones.<br />
They&rsquo;re also a testament to the continued innovation, creativity and diligence of Link Net&rsquo;s<br />
technology, product, rollout and distribution teams. The Company will continue to drive innovation<br />
of their product suite to ensure customers are provided with the best cable television and internet<br />
user experience in Indonesia.</p>

<p>Irwan Djaja, President Director and CEO, commented on the results, said: &ldquo;<em>A record set of results<br />
in 1H 2017, a testimony to the sound execution of The Company&rsquo;s strategy. We&rsquo;ve been successful<br />
in driving growth through maintaining our best in class product suite and highly effective distribution<br />
through our marketing and sales teams. Our technology and rollout divisions continue to<br />
successfully grow our world class network so that we can provide Indonesian&rsquo;s with the highest<br />
quality internet and cable television experience. This is an exciting time for our business and we<br />
will continue to innovate and provide new products and services to our customers. We&rsquo;ve had a<br />
strong first half and we&rsquo;re confident that we&rsquo;ll achieve our growth targets for 2017. I look forward<br />
to updating you on our continued success</em>&quot;.</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><u><strong>About PT Link Net Tbk</strong></u><br />
