  (68, ' Centratama Group and Linknet to Enhance Broadband Connectivity Across Indonesia', ' Centratama Group and Linknet to Enhance Broadband Connectivity Across Indonesia', ' https://www.linknet.co.id/storage/files/1newsroom/IMG_20250602_4433.jpg', ' centratama-linknet-mou', ' PT Centratama Telekomunikasi Indonesia Tbk (“Centratama”), a subsidiary of EdgePoint Infrastructure (“EdgePoint”), today announced a strategic partnership with PT Link Net Tbk (“Link Net”)', ' PT Centratama Telekomunikasi Indonesia Tbk (“Centratama”), a subsidiary of EdgePoint Infrastructure (“EdgePoint”), today announced a strategic partnership with PT Link Net Tbk (“Link Net”)', ' Ajeng', ' <p><span style="font-size:11pt; font-variant:normal; white-space:pre-wrap"><span style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000"><span style="font-weight:400"><span style="font-style:normal"><span style="text-decoration:none">PT Centratama Telekomunikasi Indonesia Tbk (&ldquo;Centratama&rdquo;), a subsidiary of EdgePoint Infrastructure (&ldquo;EdgePoint&rdquo;), today announced a strategic partnership with PT Link Net Tbk (&ldquo;Link Net&rdquo;) to support the expansion of Link Net&rsquo;s Fiber To The Home (FTTH) services on Centratama sites across Indonesia. This initiative aims to enhance the stability and expand the reach of Link Net&rsquo;s internet services, enabling more seamless and reliable connectivity for communities and businesses in key areas across the country.&nbsp;</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="line-height:1.295; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px"><span style="font-size:11pt; font-variant:normal; white-space:pre-wrap"><span style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000"><span style="font-weight:400"><span style="font-style:normal"><span style="text-decoration:none">Present at the signing ceremony were Suresh Sidhu, Chief Executive Officer of EdgePoint Infrastructure, Raymond Yan, Chief Executive Officer of Centratama, Jacopo Rigamonti, Chief of Commercial &amp; Sales Officer of Centratama, Kanishka Gayan Wickrama, Chief Executive Officer of Link Net and Yosafat Marhasak Hutagalung, Chief People and Corporate Affairs of Link Net.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="line-height:1.295; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px"><span style="font-size:11pt; font-variant:normal; white-space:pre-wrap"><span style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000"><span style="font-weight:700"><span style="font-style:normal"><span style="text-decoration:none">Raymond Yan, Chief Executive Officer of Centratama</span></span></span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:11pt; font-variant:normal; white-space:pre-wrap"><span style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000"><span style="font-weight:400"><span style="font-style:normal"><span style="text-decoration:none"> said &ldquo;This collaboration reflects our commitment to strengthening Indonesia&rsquo;s digital infrastructure and enabling greater connectivity for all. Centratama is focused on supporting the national agenda for digital transformation by delivering scalable, reliable, and future-ready solutions. We are confident that by combining our expansive site footprint with Link Net&rsquo;s strong broadband capabilities, we can accelerate the delivery of high-quality connectivity to communities and businesses across Indonesia&mdash;particularly in underserved and high-growth areas. This partnership is a key step in realizing our vision of </span></span></span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:11pt; font-variant:normal; white-space:pre-wrap"><span style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000"><span style="font-weight:400"><span style="font-style:italic"><span style="text-decoration:none">Building a Connected, Digital Indonesia</span></span></span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:11pt; font-variant:normal; white-space:pre-wrap"><span style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000"><span style="font-weight:400"><span style="font-style:normal"><span style="text-decoration:none">, where every individual and enterprise can thrive in an increasingly digital world.&rdquo;</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="line-height:1.295; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px"><span style="font-size:11pt; font-variant:normal; white-space:pre-wrap"><span style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000"><span style="font-weight:700"><span style="font-style:normal"><span style="text-decoration:none">Kanishka Gayan Wickrama, Chief Executive Officer of Link Net</span></span></span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:11pt; font-variant:normal; white-space:pre-wrap"><span style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000"><span style="font-weight:400"><span style="font-style:normal"><span style="text-decoration:none">, added &ldquo;This partnership represents a meaningful step forward in our mission to broaden the reach and reliability of our broadband services. By leveraging Centratama&rsquo;s extensive infrastructure, we aim to strengthen our operational capabilities and deliver enhanced connectivity experiences to even more customers across Indonesia. We are optimistic that this strategic collaboration will bring lasting benefits to both companies. We are also excited to translate this partnership into a concrete action plan aligned with PT Link Net Tbk&rsquo;s purpose: </span></span></span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:11pt; font-variant:normal; white-space:pre-wrap"><span style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000"><span style="font-weight:400"><span style="font-style:italic"><span style="text-decoration:none">&#39;We LINK the Nation for Better Lives&#39;.</span></span></span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:11pt; font-variant:normal; white-space:pre-wrap"><span style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000"><span style="font-weight:400"><span style="font-style:normal"><span style="text-decoration:none"> As two leading players in Indonesia&rsquo;s digital infrastructure and connectivity service industry, we are committed to working together to foster effective service integration and contribute meaningfully to the achievement of the national digital transformation agenda&rdquo;</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="line-height:1.2; text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:11pt; font-variant:normal; white-space:pre-wrap"><span style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000"><span style="font-weight:400"><span style="font-style:normal"><span style="text-decoration:none">EdgePoint Infrastructure currently owns 15,800 sites across its portfolio in Malaysia, Indonesia, and the Philippines, with Centratama making up 11,000 sites. For more information on PT Centratama Telekomunikasi Indonesia, Tbk, please visit: </span></span></span></span></span></span><a href="http://www.centratamagroup.com" style="text-decoration:none"><span style="font-size:11pt; font-variant:normal; white-space:pre-wrap"><span style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif"><span style="color:#467886"><span style="font-weight:400"><span style="font-style:normal"><span style="text-decoration:underline"><span style="-webkit-text-decoration-skip:none"><span style="text-decoration-skip-ink:none">www.centratamagroup.com</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></a><span style="font-size:11pt; font-variant:normal; white-space:pre-wrap"><span style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000"><span style="font-weight:400"><span style="font-style:normal"><span style="text-decoration:none">.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p>***</p>

<p style="line-height:1.3199999999999998; background-color:#ffffff"><span style="font-size:10pt; font-variant:normal; white-space:pre-wrap"><span style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000"><span style="font-weight:700"><span style="font-style:normal"><span style="text-decoration:none">ABOUT CENTRATAMA GROUP</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="line-height:1.3199999999999998; text-align:justify; background-color:#ffffff"><span style="font-size:10pt; font-variant:normal; white-space:pre-wrap"><span style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000"><span style="font-weight:400"><span style="font-style:normal"><span style="text-decoration:none">Under a publicly listed company of PT Centratama Telekomunikasi Indonesia, Tbk (CENT.JK), Centratama Group is a group of telecommunications infrastructure services companies which provide Tower Infrastructure and In-Building DAS (Distributed Antenna Systems) for Cellular Networks. It is currently the third largest independent towerco in Indonesia. It is a member of the EdgePoint Group, an ASEAN based independent telecommunications infrastructure company that aspires towards Building a Connected, Digital ASEAN. Headquartered in Singapore with operations in Malaysia, Indonesia and the Philippines, through EdgePoint Towers Sdn Bhd, PT Centratama Telekomunikasi Indonesia, Tbk and EdgePoints Towers Inc. respectively, the company is focused on providing sharable and leading-edge telecom structures, small cells and in-building systems. EdgePoint aims to be an industry leader through scale and innovation, driving operational efficiencies throughthe adoption of analytics and digital technologies. </span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="line-height:1.3199999999999998; text-align:justify; background-color:#ffffff">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="line-height:1.3199999999999998; text-align:justify; background-color:#ffffff"><span style="font-size:10pt; font-variant:normal; white-space:pre-wrap"><span style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000"><span style="font-weight:700"><span style="font-style:normal"><span style="text-decoration:none">ABOUT LINK NET</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="line-height:1.3199999999999998; text-align:justify; background-color:#ffffff"><span style="font-size:10pt; font-variant:normal; white-space:pre-wrap"><span style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000"><span style="font-weight:400"><span style="font-style:normal"><span style="text-decoration:none">PT Link Net Tbk (&ldquo;Link Net&rdquo;, Emitent Code: &ldquo;LINK&rdquo;) is part of Axiata Group. Link Net is dedicated to improving lives and supporting Indonesia&rsquo;s digital growth by delivering smart, reliable technology infrastructure through its three main business units. The new business units are FiberCo for fiber optic networks, EnterpriseCo for connectivity and B2B solutions, and MediaCo for content and media services. Link Net helps power the country&rsquo;s digital future. With the purpose &quot;We Link the Nation for Better Lives,&quot; the company stays focused on customers, encourages innovation and collaboration, and is committed to constantly getting better, aiming to deliver great results in everything it does. The Company has a network within greater Jakarta, greater Bandung, greater Surabaya (include Malang, Gresik, Sidoarjo), Bali, Serang-Cilegon, Semarang, Solo, Medan, Batam, Cikampek-Purwakarta, Cirebon, Tegal, Yogyakarta, dan Kediri.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>', ' <p><span style="font-size:11pt; font-variant:normal; white-space:pre-wrap"><span style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000"><span style="font-weight:400"><span style="font-style:normal"><span style="text-decoration:none">PT Centratama Telekomunikasi Indonesia Tbk (&ldquo;Centratama&rdquo;), a subsidiary of EdgePoint Infrastructure (&ldquo;EdgePoint&rdquo;), today announced a strategic partnership with PT Link Net Tbk (&ldquo;Link Net&rdquo;) to support the expansion of Link Net&rsquo;s Fiber To The Home (FTTH) services on Centratama sites across Indonesia. This initiative aims to enhance the stability and expand the reach of Link Net&rsquo;s internet services, enabling more seamless and reliable connectivity for communities and businesses in key areas across the country.&nbsp;</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

