<p style="line-height:1.295; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px"><span style="font-size:11pt; font-variant:normal; white-space:pre-wrap"><span style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000"><span style="font-weight:700"><span style="font-style:normal"><span style="text-decoration:none">Raymond Yan, Chief Executive Officer of Centratama</span></span></span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:11pt; font-variant:normal; white-space:pre-wrap"><span style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000"><span style="font-weight:400"><span style="font-style:normal"><span style="text-decoration:none"> said &ldquo;This collaboration reflects our commitment to strengthening Indonesia&rsquo;s digital infrastructure and enabling greater connectivity for all. Centratama is focused on supporting the national agenda for digital transformation by delivering scalable, reliable, and future-ready solutions. We are confident that by combining our expansive site footprint with Link Net&rsquo;s strong broadband capabilities, we can accelerate the delivery of high-quality connectivity to communities and businesses across Indonesia&mdash;particularly in underserved and high-growth areas. This partnership is a key step in realizing our vision of </span></span></span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:11pt; font-variant:normal; white-space:pre-wrap"><span style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000"><span style="font-weight:400"><span style="font-style:italic"><span style="text-decoration:none">Building a Connected, Digital Indonesia</span></span></span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:11pt; font-variant:normal; white-space:pre-wrap"><span style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000"><span style="font-weight:400"><span style="font-style:normal"><span style="text-decoration:none">, where every individual and enterprise can thrive in an increasingly digital world.&rdquo;</span></span></span></s